<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recipe Details</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: brightness(70%);
        }

        .header h1 {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
            z-index: 2;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content strong {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        button {
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #c0392b;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="<%= @recipe.image_url %>" alt="Recipe Image">
            <h1><%= @recipe.title %></h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Ингредиенты:</strong> <%= @recipe.ingredients %></p>
            <p><strong>Инструкции:</strong> <%= @recipe.instructions %></p>
            <p><strong>Время приготовления:</strong> <%= @recipe.preparation_time %> минут</p>
            <p><strong>Сложность:</strong> <%= @recipe.difficulty %></p>
            <p><strong>Категория:</strong> <%= @recipe.category_id %></p>

            <div class="buttons">
                <form action="/recipes/<%= @recipe.id %>" method="POST" style="margin: 0;">
                    <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
                    <button type="submit">Удалить рецепт</button>
                </form>
                <a href="/">Вернуться на главную</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
